title: 250. Andy & DJ CTI: Black Panther Director Arrested, No Jail Time For Injecting Patients & U.S. Biolabs In Ukraine
itunes:title: 250. Andy & DJ CTI: Black Panther Director Arrested, No Jail Time For Injecting Patients & U.S. Biolabs In Ukraine
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss "Black Panther" director Ryan Coogler being mistaken for a bank robber & arrested after attempting to withdraw $12,000 discreetly with a note, no jail time for a biotech executive who administered his own fake Covid-19 vaccine, and Russia revealing the United States has Biolabs with plague & anthrax in Ukraine.
